歐洲老麥都比香港黎講真係好貴 食個包都成50蚊"},{"pid":"b1aa619c57d225b5617f93ed88edddd813733c3c","tid":211352,"uid":91399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T15:19:56.000Z","msg":"明明啱啱出脆香雞翼嗰陣我同阿爸去食仲笑9脆香雞翼係小兒麻痺咁，邊有人買<br />\n點知依家上咗癮<br />\n上星期食咗三次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68d841799a7b74b8287c3f5eb8edccccab6c98d1","tid":211352,"uid":61974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T15:26:33.000Z","msg":"放到淋晒都咁好食<br />\n唔敢想像佢新鮮炸出黎既脆香雞翼會係咩感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"128050806ba11146038a0688d0615ad9d90960cd","tid":211352,"uid":85785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T15:28:30.000Z","msg":"岩岩食完 脆香雞翼有麥香雞既味 好難食<br />\n第一次食到吐返出黎"},{"pid":"7e6b4f6d2b989c20575320ddb8b6fc8e4739cafd","tid":211352,"uid":91399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T15:31:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>放到淋晒都咁好食<br />\n唔敢想像佢新鮮炸出黎既脆香雞翼會係咩感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n以前做老麥<br />\n試過真係一炸起就食<br />\n雞翼入面啲雞油爆出嚟超正<br />\n<br />\n次次返夜更洗廚房必定攞返起碼20隻雞翼返屋企J"},{"pid":"ab7b18cb303585866d728d974baea4f7d9f7a9ca","tid":211352,"uid":4679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T15:38:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>放到淋晒都咁好食<br />\n唔敢想像佢新鮮炸出黎既脆香雞翼會係咩感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好運嘅話係新鮮炸起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 通常係凌晨時分機會大啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a11ac246483d716c41a260574473a3a2aba8d909","tid":211352,"uid":4679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T15:39:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>放到淋晒都咁好食<br />\n唔敢想像佢新鮮炸出黎既脆香雞翼會係咩感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n以前做老麥<br />\n試過真係一炸起就食<br />\n雞翼入面啲雞油爆出嚟超正<br />\n<br />\n次次返夜更洗廚房必定攞返起碼20隻雞翼返屋企J</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 20隻真係可以慢慢嘆"},{"pid":"fd77f595aff48f9255b0e97631a00794b01657c3","tid":211352,"uid":4679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T15:41:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雖然歐洲食嘢係貴 但係歐洲老麥都比香港黎講真係好貴 食個包都成50蚊</blockquote><br />\n都幾貴下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 份量會唔會大過香港好多"},{"pid":"a2fa60b3a7a4b80e5757162305c2113c50db6aa4","tid":211352,"uid":12111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T17:09:50.000Z","msg":"好掛住香草辣雞翼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db544d6a18b886dd54eaae2dcd67e6597572a166","tid":211352,"uid":4679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T17:25:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好掛住香草辣雞翼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢都好掛住你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n琴晚食咗真係冇得輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6e4f21e41b55f2c919f606e265c18cb843b66d4","tid":211352,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T01:04:06.000Z","msg":"香草辣雞翼辣左好多"},{"pid":"bc3ec3647ebec648790b5569e0e4b75536ba839f","tid":211352,"uid":41614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T01:14:07.000Z","msg":"香草辣雞翼一定係世界第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d9348e3f6cbe5ded4e91305269d90870cd152f5","tid":211352,"uid":82304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T08:08:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香草辣雞翼一定係世界第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係正撚到！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}